{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b2daae0728","title":"在《农村社会主义教育运动中目前提出的一些问题》未定稿中加写的三段话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0a4e4ea5df","index":0,"year":1965,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"b2daae0728","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指导理论","id":"c1c0033e04","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fa61399deb","type":"title","text":"在《农村社会主义教育运动中目前提出的一些问题》未定稿中加写的三段话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b2daae0728","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"658a9e8165","type":"paragraph","text":"在《农村社会主义教育运动中目前提出的一些问题》未定稿中加写的三段话","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b2daae0728","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"95b0f2cf19","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b2daae0728","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"778e67d844","type":"paragraph","text":"1965.01.00","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b2daae0728","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"87d52f45b8","type":"paragraph","text":"这两种提法，不说是什么社会里四清四不清矛盾，也不说是什么党的内外矛盾交叉。从字面上看来，所谓四清四不清过去历史上什么社会里也能用；所谓党内外矛盾交叉，什么党派也能用；都没有说明今天矛盾的性质，因此不是马克思列宁主义的。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b2daae0728","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e016fbc784","type":"paragraph","text":"忘记十几年来我党的这一条基本理论和基本实践，就会要走到斜路上去。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b2daae0728","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"91a04bd530","type":"paragraph","text":"城市中社会主义教育运动过去称五反运动，以后通称四清运动，取消“五反”的名称。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b2daae0728","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}